Those exercises have the goal to get practice with a microservice infrastructure 
and understand the difference between asynchronous and an asynchronous connection in microservices context.

Execrcises
- Implements a CRUD functions that manage the favorites articles in the application, profiled!
- Create Statistics service that give a list of articles ordered by favorites
- Implements resilience4j rule to prevent error if some service is down
- Refactor this infra-microservice comuncation with rabbit mq and see difference!
